snippet.title: Classic Game Room reviews MATH GRAN PRIX for Atari 2600
snippet.description:
Classic Game Room Season 2 - Episode 5

Edit Station 1, the Classic Game Room's dead editing system, reviews Math Gran Prix for Atari 2600.... or does he?

Game Room reviewed Atari, NES, Nintendo, Sega Genesis, Dreamcast and Playstation... too bad they didn't get to Xbox 360, PS3, PS2 or Wii.
